{
  "openapi": "3.0.1",
  "info": {
    "title": "Nova Case Service",
    "description": "The Nova case service exposes the case information and performs operations on case objects.\r\n\r\nFollowing are the DTOs that are common across many services:\r\n\r\n**ExternalIdentifierDTO fields**\r\n\r\nNova case identifiers are defined in this Data Transfer Object (DTO).  \r\n  * id1: *Case reference number*\r\n  * id2: *Case previous number*\r\n\r\n**AdditionalIdentifierDTO fields**\r\n\r\nCase additional information. \r\n  * id1: *Joint case number*\r\n",
    "version": "20.1.141.0"
  },
  "servers": [
    {
      "url": "/tieto/collection/casesvc"
    }
  ],
  "paths": {
